Title   : GMR Airports, Cyient among 8 stocks showing bullish White Marubozu Pattern 
Source  : economictimes.indiatimes.com
Published: 2025-09-17T04:09:55
Fetched : 2025-09-17T05:39:34.351827
URL     : https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/markets/stocks/news/gmr-airports-cyient-among-8-stocks-showing-bullish-white-marubozu-pattern/slideshow/123934949.cms
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
On September 16, eight Nifty500 stocks triggered the bullish “White Marubozu” scanner, according to stockedge.com’s technical scan data.
A White Marubozu is a bullish candlestick pattern in technical analysis. It forms when the opening price is the lowest and the closing price is the highest for the given period.
Depicted by a long white (or green) candlestick with no upper shadow and a small or absent lower shadow, it reflects strong buying pressure throughout the session. Traders view it as a signal that buyers dominated from open to close, often using the pattern to guide future trading decisions.

